news.title: Jaipur development body to upload approved maps of highrise buildings
news.para: The decision was taken to keep a better coordination among various civic body’s department including town planning, enforcement wing and zones offices.

news.title: Ahmedabad: Iscon-Ambli stretch sees Rs 1,500 crore land transactions in past year
news.para: In fact, the high street saw some fast and furious real estate action following the ebbing of second wave of pandemic with the four kilometre stretch from Iscon Crossroads to Bopal Junction recording at least a dozen major land transactions worth Rs 1,500 crore in the past year.

news.title: Gurugram: Mahira Homes buyers stage protest, seek flat possession
news.para: More than 1,500 homebuyers, most of whom have already paid 100% of the amount, have been left in the lurch since DTCP cancelled the licence of the project and recommended registration of an FIR against Mahira Infratech Pvt Ltd for “forging documents and fabricating bank guarantees”.
